               <p>ROBERT BEAME. On the 27th of January, I was in <placeName id="t18250217-132-crimeloc770">Smithfield</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18250217-132-crimeloc770" type="placeName" value="Smithfield"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18250217-132-crimeloc770" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250217-132-off768 t18250217-132-crimeloc770"></join>, and felt a handkerchief drawn from my pocket. I turned round, and saw it in the prisoner's hand. I collared him, and he dropped it on the ground.</p>
